  "summary": "Malicious code in ogd-platform (npm)",
  "details": "Ogd-platform@1.0.0 contains no functional code — only a preinstall lifecycle hook in package.json. On npm install, the hook runs hostname, whoami, and pwd to collect host system information, then exfiltrates this data via curl POST to hxxps://webhook[.]site/1ea0386f-dcc0-4f1b-bdbb-61732d6535fb/ogd-platform (a webhook[.]site endpoint commonly used for data collection).",
